Name: Suspicious Crisp Croissant Combo
Desc: A small pastry-and-coffee combo. The stony bread stands solid against your teeth, having seemingly been robbed of all moisture. The bitter drink stained with sourness is such that you'd be pardoned for thinking it some kind of medicinal concoction. The only saving grace is that this isn't the main course...
Effect: Decreases all party members' climbing and sprinting Stamina consumption by 15% for 900s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
